IRS990.MissionDesc: Futurewise works throughout Washington State implementing smart growth strategies to create healthy livable communities, protect our working farmlands, forests, and waterways, and to ensure a better quality of life for present and future generations.
IRS990.Desc: Futurewise is committed to preventing the loss of Washington State's most valuable natural resource lands, ensuring clean healthy water, providing housing for all people at all income levels, and making it possible for people to walk, bike and take transit. Futurewise worked across the state to respond to these pressing economic, equity and environmental challenges through its research, engagement, planning & design, policy, advocacy and legal work.
